SOFTDEV IT111 Group 05 Lectors and Commentators Ministry for the Archdiocese of Manila - Angsalitangdiyos.com
The project aims to provide a tool that helps online users to identify the designated dates of religious lections and feasts within a specified year.
Create a database that includes (e.g. Solemnities or Feasts, Events, Seasons of Lent, Advent and Easter, etc.) within the year
Create a tool to insert the specified events that are specified by the Catholic church
Create a tool that shows the readings of the said database for the benefit of the client
Provide a calendar to display links to the necessary pages and/or audio files, representing lections and mass readings for each date
Encourage the online community to visit the AngSalitaNgDiyos.com site for informative and spiritual purposes
Is a community for the Lectors and Commentators of different parishes that is under the archdioceses of Manila.

To evangelize and catechize the people of the Archdiocese of Manila of their participation to the evangelical task of the universal Church by providing liturgical formation and ministries they can participate in.
Rev. Fr. Carmelo P. Arada Jr
